{"tid":1178543,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU興奮突襲生日應援 發現粉絲全走下秒崩","createTime":"2019-05-30T13:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T15:06:52.000Z","uid":34643,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6efc7fb50a07519fbbe0a30e43b1cd6426576098","tid":1178543,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w0iBntma9GQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw0iBntma9GQ&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1bQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=197602fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w0iBntma9GQ</a><br />\n<br />\n最近忙於拍劇的IU，在生日當天早早起床，約了父母吃飯，晚上還打算突襲官方生日應援<br />\nCafe，給粉絲們驚喜。不過未給到粉絲驚喜，IU就先自己崩潰了！<br />\n<br />\nIU在生日當天親自突襲了官方生日應援活動，說了一大堆開場白後，興奮地跑上樓給粉絲<br />\n驚喜。在環視了一周未公開自拍的場内佈置後，卻依舊不見任何一人，崩潰地在樓梯問了<br />\n句「全部人都走了？」然後委屈地坐在樓梯上，畫面令經理人和PD笑不停。IU甚至懷疑，<br />\n是不是夜晚8時後就有人負責趕走所有粉絲，又委屈巴巴地怪PD：「為什麽不告訴大家我<br />\n要來。<br />\n<br />\n最終有工作人員通知IU有兩個粉絲在樓上，IU才重露笑顔，開心地去見粉絲。IU親自為兩<br />\n位粉絲送上小卡，之後再上3樓去見其他仍在的粉絲並閒聊。其後有粉絲分享後記，指IU<br />\n和粉絲們聊了很多，而且拍照的要求全不拒絕，十分寵粉呢！"},{"pid":"e565d17c1ee770d4f86995757baf412b7ec167c8","tid":1178543,"uid":3303,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6efc7fb50a07519fbbe0a30e43b1cd6426576098","tid":1178543,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w0iBntma9GQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw0iBntma9GQ&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1bQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=197602fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w0iBntma9GQ</a><br />\n<br />\n最近忙於拍劇的IU，在生日當天早早起床，約了父母吃飯，晚上還打算突襲官方生日應援<br />\nCafe，給粉絲們驚喜。不過未給到粉絲驚喜，IU就先自己崩潰了！<br />\n<br />\nIU在生日當天親自突襲了官方生日應援活動，說了一大堆開場白後，興奮地跑上樓給粉絲<br />\n驚喜。在環視了一周未公開自拍的場内佈置後，卻依舊不見任何一人，崩潰地在樓梯問了<br />\n句「全部人都走了？」然後委屈地坐在樓梯上，畫面令經理人和PD笑不停。IU甚至懷疑，<br />\n是不是夜晚8時後就有人負責趕走所有粉絲，又委屈巴巴地怪PD：「為什麽不告訴大家我<br />\n要來。<br />\n<br />\n最終有工作人員通知IU有兩個粉絲在樓上，IU才重露笑顔，開心地去見粉絲。IU親自為兩<br />\n位粉絲送上小卡，之後再上3樓去見其他仍在的粉絲並閒聊。其後有粉絲分享後記，指IU<br />\n和粉絲們聊了很多，而且拍照的要求全不拒絕，十分寵粉呢！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:11:47.000Z","msg":"可愛"},{"pid":"91be8411d5340890b1dfc8902c1cbae1776aeabb","tid":1178543,"uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:13:15.000Z","msg":"1:16 扁嘴扭計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3266908b3abc4c791cca10e6ae53a9ed7405a0a0","tid":1178543,"uid":2615,"like":7,"dislike":43,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"臭雞一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3859fd71a8a65141236f924f8371c6d96839c7","tid":1178543,"uid":36236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:16:34.000Z","msg":"成段片個feel都好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792494d41607b9496f05e315e53bf2c6b61a1f86","tid":1178543,"uid":227992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:20:30.000Z","msg":"時間一到，無人係正常喎。"},{"pid":"59054112cded0214c909d0458f6e37a32704ef8c","tid":1178543,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91be8411d5340890b1dfc8902c1cbae1776aeabb","tid":1178543,"uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:13:15.000Z","msg":"1:16 扁嘴扭計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:28:11.000Z","msg":"扭慣我計 冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1162627e117f69186dcd00e1e9170763abf1167","tid":1178543,"uid":150649,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3266908b3abc4c791cca10e6ae53a9ed7405a0a0","tid":1178543,"uid":2615,"like":7,"dislike":43,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"臭雞一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/